parameters.name: ConfigurationName
parameters.description: Name of the network analyzer configuration.

nested_items.name: TraceContent
nested_items.description: Trace content for your wireless devices, gateways, and multicast groups.

nested_items.name: WirelessDeviceFrameInfo
nested_items.description: FrameInfo of your wireless device resources for the trace content. Use FrameInfo to debug the communication between your LoRaWAN end devices and the network server.

nested_items.name: LogLevel
nested_items.description: The log level for a log message. The log levels can be disabled, or set to ERROR to display less verbose logs containing only error information, or to INFO for more detailed logs.

nested_items.name: MulticastFrameInfo
nested_items.description: FrameInfo of your multicast group resources for the trace content. Use FrameInfo to debug the multicast communication between your multicast groups and the network server.

nested_items.name: WirelessDevices
nested_items.description: List of wireless device resources that have been added to the network analyzer configuration.

nested_items.name: WirelessGateways
nested_items.description: List of wireless gateway resources that have been added to the network analyzer configuration.

nested_items.name: Description
nested_items.description: The description of the new resource.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name of the new resource.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: Name of the network analyzer configuration.

nested_items.name: MulticastGroups
nested_items.description: List of multicast group resources that have been added to the network analyzer configuration.
